Disappearing Comments?
text: Just out of curiousity, under what circumstances do comments completely disappear from HN threads?   I recently posted a comment that several people found offensive to the HN culture and rules.  Some comments called me out for my word choice, or the sentiment I expressed.   Some agreed.   In  two or three cases, where I responded to criticism with an explanation of my intent and and apology for the unintended offense, and one where I simply agreed with the interlocutor, the comments - both my response and the one I was responding are now gone.   How does this happen?
